  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This magical shield is imbued with properties befitting a worshipper of Tymora, and its use is limited to those of chaotic good alignment.\n\nTymora is the goddess of good fortune, skill, and victory. She is the patron of adventurers in general. She is fickle in her nature, and chaotic good in alignment. \n\nThe battle cry of Tymora's followers is \"fortune favors the bold.\" A brave heart and willingness to take risk will beat a carefully wrought plan nine times out of ten. Thus, while not foolish, Tymora's followers will often throw caution to the wind and trust in luck. One must place oneself in the hands of fate (meaning Tymora's) and trust to one's own luck.\n\n"
    }
  },
